reviewText: In this movie you will learn that none lives in this Englishman's home!  You will also learn about some famous racehorses from back in the day!  You will see A study,A library,A studio and A rose garden!

This series, An Englishman's Home is superb.  Why though is it not available in DVD format?  Hopefully it will be soon as there is so much interest in historic homes and, again, this series is truly excellent.
